23 Aug 97

asa.c, readme.ms:
ASA_RESOLUTION acts at max and min boundaries similar to how integers
are treated.  ASA_RESOLUTION takes precedence over parameter_type []
when parameter_type [] is integral when calculating new generated
parameters.

